extendedInfo.description: >Introducing TablematesA new rewards program from Outback Steakhouse where you can earn free food for yourself and earn it faster with your friends.**NOTE: Currently only available in Boston, MA; Chicago, IL; Phoenix, AZ; Norfolk, VA; and Michigan. Coming soon to more markets.  Join now, it's free and easy.Just for downloading the app and signing up you get:* A free dessert for your birthday* Access to free food every month (or what we like to call Monthly Perks)* The ability to earn free food even faster when you link up with friends in an online TableEarn on your own:* Youâll earn 1 point for every $1 spent. Points can be redeemed for free food, like a free dessert, free  appetizer, a free steak dinner or even $ off your check.* You are automatically eligible for Monthly Perks, which give you access to free menu items once a month to enjoy with family and friends. Just choose your occasion.* Free Appetizer: Order one of our appetizers and get another free * $10 off Two Entrees: Order two entrees and get $10 off* Free Appetizer and Dessert: Just order two entrees and get an  appetizer and dessert for free
